<item>
            <title>[LU-182] RHEL6 support is broken</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-182</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;LDISKFS-fs (loop0): Unrecognized mount option &quot;64bithash&quot; or missing value&lt;br/&gt;
LustreError: 2483:0:(obd_mount.c:1394:server_kernel_mount()) ll_kern_mount failed: rc = -22&lt;br/&gt;
LustreError: 2483:0:(obd_mount.c:1675:server_fill_super()) Unable to mount device /dev/loop0: -22&lt;br/&gt;
LustreError: 2483:0:(obd_mount.c:2149:lustre_fill_super()) Unable to mount  (-22)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;64bithash is only referenced in ext&lt;/p&gt;
{3,4}
&lt;p&gt;-export-64bit-name-hash.patch which are not part of rhel6 series.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
